Tamil conversations, music and ideas designed to help people own their attention.
</p>

</div>

</section>

</Layout>

<style>
.hero{
text-align:center;
}

.eyebrow{
letter-spacing:4px;
text-transform:uppercase;
font-size:14px;
color:#888;
margin-bottom:24px;
}

.subtitle{
font-size:32px;
margin-top:30px;
color:#d0d0d0;
}

.center{
